Modifications introduced by this fork (under copilot-cli/) port the upstream
agents, skills, slash commands, and MCP connector templates to the GitHub
Copilot CLI as an installable extension and plugin marketplace. The Claude
Cowork plugins and Managed Agent cookbooks under plugins/ and
managed-agent-cookbooks/ are mirrored from upstream as the single source of
truth for the Copilot CLI port; install those from the upstream repository.

